{"tid":2402253,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男教師被控襲警 被襲警稱認不出同僚 今裁定教師罪名不成立 訟費申請獲批","createTime":"2021-02-10T10:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T15:28:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ec562ae9880b4edbdd855606bd4e937bddf543fd","tid":2402253,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13613&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=564abd4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13613</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第八庭<br />\n#鄧少雄裁判官 #裁決<br />\n👤陳(27) #0908銅鑼灣 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n違反香港法例第212章《侵害人身罪條例》第36(b)條。陳手足被控於2019年9月8日在銅鑼灣港鐵站F1出口外，襲擊在正當執行職務的警員14212趙金。 #襲警 <br />\n<br />\n法庭裁定被告罪名不成立，辯方訟費申請獲批。"},{"pid":"24c390e63f8c81f4e0a1a6fc1f934a52cfa7c9c4","tid":2402253,"uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:21:26.000Z","msg":"2019年9月8日銅鑼灣一帶爆發警民衝突，其間一名27歲男教師涉在港鐵銅鑼灣站外遭警員追截時，用右拳頭打其左邊面一下，導致其面部紅痛。他否認一項襲警罪，於東區裁判法院受審。警員供稱，案發時場面混亂，當時只知一名軍裝警員為被告套上膠手扣，後來才從他人口中得知是一名軍裝警長，裁判官鄧少雄直言「梗係啦，都無number（警員編號），梗係認唔到啦」。<br />\n<br />\n警員14212趙金供稱，當晚見一身穿藍短袖上衣的男子大叫「黑社會」、「黑警死全家」等口號，在場的人和應，其間看見一名軍裝警員欲搭該男子膊頭，男子突然轉身，從渣甸坊行人路向希慎廣場跑，他追截12米後用雙手捉男子的腰側，其間失平衡，雙雙倒地，男子背向地、面向天，兩人身貼身，趙金壓住男子，對方不斷掙扎，其間男子用右拳頭打趙金左邊面一下，導致其面部紅痛。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">辯方盤問趙金時指出，被告打中他什麼部位，趙金先稱是左眼顴骨位置，後改稱顴骨和眼角之間，又稱兩處都有傷。至於被告用拳頭哪一部分擊中他，趙金表示不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n另趙金曾供稱「軍裝警想搭住男子膊頭」，惟趙金在供辭上稱「搭到膊頭」，辯方質疑「搭住可解無掂到，呢個係你對中文嘅理解？」，趙金回應「我寫錯咗，我承認」。辯方又稱，趙金於案發時已當警員8年，寫口供是「家常便飯」，趙金表示同意，又說「因為我學歷低，所以寫得差」。</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8081204e6adb63a53f171d66b25f251d054f927","tid":2402253,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dc9effd09a7ffccc01923027366438e3dfdc05","tid":2402253,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8081204e6adb63a53f171d66b25f251d054f927","tid":2402253,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9439ab1a14411334433114b308ffff6e7253b716","tid":2402253,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:28:53.000Z","msg":"「梗係啦，都無number（警員編號），梗係認唔到啦」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255413094df1ee9aacee4fb10d389a8b19782297","tid":2402253,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64dc9effd09a7ffccc01923027366438e3dfdc