ces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"人滿為患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26788c1d4f3aad56cb4f827de0e8cc3f85558ba","tid":2402253,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"趙金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吞食天地d肥閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091b2ac6cd98ab07f71d343d22fa236fc7b5d4c1","tid":2402253,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:09:47.000Z","msg":"濫捕，老屈，濫告"},{"pid":"c0a18ec3d3382e1614ee20e8878a8e30d69a6e19","tid":2402253,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"黑警+律政狗=曱甴集團"},{"pid":"e8650f1d9bf3a1b9ad07415254d5a1b92f826f02","tid":2402253,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230a693921e0338145156b243cd8fdc7b0d21c49","tid":2402253,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"cee1f498fad2bc4b852ece66c3468a846cc79246","tid":2402253,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"月經：香港警察就是狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2340238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2340238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔知覆咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b066f98e27846f7c380055977a8b7873a651c43c","tid":2402253,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:28:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=trF9oH9BR-s&amp;t=79s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtrF9oH9BR-s%26t%3D79s&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=01af0774\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=trF9oH9BR-s&amp;t=79s</a>"},{"pid":"d11220d5111d756afcedcf7c8bc9a4879222a3fc","tid":2402253,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:49:53.000Z","msg":"2019年9月8日晚港島區多處有警民衝突，一名27歲男教師涉嫌當晚在港鐵銅鑼灣站外襲警，被控一項襲擊在正當執行職務之警務人員罪。他否認控罪，經審訊後今（7日）在東區法院獲裁定罪名不成立，裁判官鄧少雄認為控方案情充滿疑點，加上警員的傷勢與證供不符，故判被告脫罪兼獲訟費。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指，控方的案情充滿疑點，令法庭難以接納。警員趙金聲稱當時從後捉住被告腰間的衣服，而兩人當時均向前跑，故被告倒地時理應是面向地下，而非如他所指的「背向地下」。趙在作供時聲稱不知道被告是如何轉了身，惟他當時和被告近距離接觸，理應集中全副精神在被告身上，但他卻無法解釋被告如何180度轉身，並不合理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，鄧官亦留意到趙面部的傷勢主要由2至3粒紅點組成，似被細小硬物壓成傷痕，而不是被人揮拳所致。因此，他裁定被告罪名不成立。"},{"pid":"df8dea041db12db2de3c918e531b3dabc484fc6c","tid":2402253,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"官難明警員為何向前飛撲卻會四腳朝天<br />\n<br />\n鄧官不接納兩名警員的證供。鄧官指出，趙姓警員與被告均向前奔跑，警員從後撲向被告，當時左手抓住被告左腰側，右手抓住被告右腰側；法庭難以明白警員為何最終會四腳朝天而不是面向地面。另外，兩人近距離接觸，警員應該全副精神專注制服被告，不可能觀察到被告如何180度轉身。<br />\n<br />\n警員曾自認因學歷低故口供寫得差<br />\n<br />\n控方以被告行為自招嫌疑為由，反對訟費申請。辯方反指當時警員說話召喚被告「過來」是挑釁在先，被告才作對答式的回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/6KQEM2EBLNFG7IDXGIXNP74IPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2F6KQEM2EBLNFG7IDXGIXNP74IPU%2F&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=70f3504b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2F6KQEM2EBLNFG7IDXGIXNP74IPU%2F&h=78dda4a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/6KQEM2EBLNFG7IDXGIXNP74IPU/</a>"},{"pid":"c1c10d90e86494d3f7c7f13fb78db4fc482717d5","tid":2402253,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8fa2d59d87d4b3083a11de1bf857e55abed90c","tid":2402253,"uid":30113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾仆街黑警"}]}